# .agents — Project Context for AI Coding Assistants

## Project Overview

This is a fullstack TypeScript monorepo ("tsProject") with:
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express 5 + Prisma ORM + PostgreSQL
- **Frontend**: React 19 + Vite 8 + TailwindCSS 4 + React Router v7
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (via Docker Compose), schema managed by Prisma

---

## Repository Structure

```
tsProject/
├── backend/                  # Express API server
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── config/           # DB connection (Prisma client)
│   │   ├── controllers/      # Request orchestration layer
│   │   ├── routes/           # Express route definitions
│   │   └── services/         # Business logic & Prisma queries
│   ├── prisma/
│   │   ├── schema.prisma     # Database schema
│   │   └── migrations/       # Auto-generated Prisma migrations
│   ├── generated/            # Prisma generated client (DO NOT edit manually)
│   ├── main.ts               # Script entrypoint (seed/test runner)
│   ├── server.ts             # Express app entrypoint
│   ├── prisma.config.ts      # Prisma config
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── docker-compose.yml
│   ├── .env                  # Environment variables (not committed)
│   └── .env.example          # Template for .env
│
├── frontend/                 # React SPA
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/       # React components (Home, Get, Login, Destinos)
│   │   ├── App.tsx           # Root component
│   │   ├── main.tsx          # React DOM entry
│   │   └── routes.tsx        # React Router route definitions
│   ├── public/
│   ├── index.html
│   └── vite.config.ts
│
├── generated/                # Shared generated output (root level)
├── tsconfig.json             # Root TypeScript config
└── package.json              # Root workspace package.json
```

